@startuml door_open_warn_to_comfort_profile_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Door Open Warn To Comfort Profile Signal Flow\n(Door leaf states -> BCM -> Body comfort state)

participant "Door / Tailgate leaves\nFL/FR/RL/RR + Tailgate" as Doors #F4F7FB
participant "BCM\ndoor + comfort owner" as BCM #E8F7E8
participant "Body gateway / comfort frames" as BodyBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / Panels" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Door-State Aggregation ==

Doors -> BCM : gDoorFlOpenState / LockState\n... gDoorRrOpenState / LockState\nTailgateOpenState
BCM -> BCM : build doorStateMask
BCM -> BCM : derive doorLockState
BCM -> BCM : if any door open or tailgate open\nthen doorOpenWarn = 1
note right of BCM
Representative door seams
- DoorStateMask
- DoorLockState
- DoorOpenWarn
end note

== Body Door Publication ==

BCM -> BodyBus : frmDoorStateMsg
BCM -> BCM : output DoorStateMask /\nDoorLockState / DoorOpenWarn

== Comfort Profile Derivation ==

BCM -> BCM : if stale inputs -> comfortProfile = 0
BCM -> BCM : else if remote climate / seat comfort -> 3
BCM -> BCM : else if door command / open door / unlocked /\nPAAK access -> 2
BCM -> BCM : else if driveState > 0 or ambientMode > 0 -> 4
BCM -> BCM : else default -> 1
BCM -> BCM : comfortStatus / comfortError
note right of BCM
Representative comfort output
- frmBodyComfortStateMsg
- ComfortProfile / Status / Error
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

BCM -> BodyBus : frmBodyComfortStateMsg
BCM -> Obs : write trace / panel readback

note over Doors, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Door leaf states enter BCM
2. BCM derives DoorOpenWarn from door/tailgate openness
3. BCM folds access/open/lock state into ComfortProfile
4. Door state and comfort state are published as separate body frames
end note

@enduml
